ikad složiti.

00:17:34.460 --> 00:17:38.740
Ali, skoro da sam siguran da te
nikad više neću upucati.

00:17:38.820 --> 00:17:41.660
Jedini način da bi bio siguran
je da ti mene upucaš.

00:17:41.740 --> 00:17:44.780
Uvek sam se slagao
za poštenu kaznu.

00:17:44.860 --> 00:17:48.580
Evo ti.

00:17:50.380 --> 00:17:52.780
Uradi to. Upucaj me.

00:17:54.020 --> 00:17:56.260
