to. Baš tu.

00:17:59.980 --> 00:18:01.940
To je jedini način.

00:18:02.020 --> 00:18:04.620
Ok.

00:18:04.700 --> 00:18:06.780
- Lagao si!

00:18:06.860 --> 00:18:09.900
Mrtav si, čoveče!

